<li><a href="Grammy_Awards_of_2007" title="Grammy Awards of 2007" class="mw-redirect">Grammy Awards of 2007</a> - <a href="Grammy_Award_for_Song_of_the_Year#2000s" title="Grammy Award for Song of the Year">Song of the Year</a>, "<a href="Jesus,_Take_the_Wheel" title="Jesus, Take the Wheel">Jesus, Take the Wheel</a>" (Nomination)</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Juno Awards
